MALALANE &#8211; Golfer, Pablo Larrazabal posted a notice on his Twitter account late yesterday afternoon confirming the death of Carlos Pigem&#8217;s caddie.Argentinian Pedro Ramseyer was in his 60s. It has been reported that he suffered a heart attack in his room in a bed and breakfast in Malalane.He shared a room with Basil van Rooyen, the caddie for Thomas Aiken, who found him unresponsive in bed yesterday morning.The Alfred Dunhill Championship started at Leopard Creek yesterday.Pablo Larrazabal&#8217;s Twitter account.&nbsp;&nbsp;Pedro Ramseyer. Photo: Instagram